<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-9585] CompilerConfiguration copy constructor does not copy compilation customizers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-9585</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Consider the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.codehaus.groovy.control.*
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.codehaus.groovy.control.customizers.*

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; config = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; CompilerConfiguration()
config.addCompilationCustomizers(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ImportCustomizer().tap {
  addStarImport(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;groovy.transform&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
})

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; clone = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; CompilerConfiguration(config)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; clone.getCompilationCustomizers().size() == 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Trying to copy from a base config (like one set up by STC and SC unit tests) results in missing the compilation customizers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
