                            <comment id="17132796" author="paulk" created="Thu, 11 Jun 2020 00:08:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The changes for this are relatively simple but when applied break gradle somehow.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;org.gradle.api.internal.tasks.compile.ApiGroovyCompiler$TrackingClassGenerationCompilationCustomizer&lt;/tt&gt; is throwing an NPE and &lt;tt&gt;:groovy-macro:compileGroovy&lt;/tt&gt; fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d guess gradle is using the copy constructor and assuming that the new config has no customizers but I haven&apos;t tracked it down fully yet, so it could be something else.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
